title: The One Where Lala Says The F Word A LOT
description:
A series of unfortunate events that actually started Sunday night, led to this podcast episode! Details include WiFi failure, a locked bathroom door, a highly unpleasant encounter in the parking lot of Ocean’s pediatrician, a podcast episode with Katie Maloney that didn’t actually record, a missed birthday, and Lisa coming “this close” to losing a toe! But there some happy moments too involving Ocean, Jax & Brittany, and Scheana Shay’s lash line launch! And Lala answers more of your voicemails!
